     <div type="book_to_author">
   <head>The Bookes aunswer.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>VVHat as of right I ought to do, performed that shalbe,</l>
      <l>And therefore gentle Readers all, that me shall ouersee,</l>
      <l>I doe beseech you earnestlie, my Maister to excuse,</l>
      <l>And pardon his inuention rude, his meeters and his Muse:</l>
      <l>For I dare vndertake for him, that thankfull he will rest,</l>
      <l>If of your kindly courtesie he may be full possest.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
